{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/kembali-ke-masa-depan-lewat-manga-back-to-the-future/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Kembali Ke Masa Depan Lewat Manga Back To The Future","content":"<p>Back To The Future adalah salah satu film sains fiksi fenomenal dan punya pengaruh besar hingga hari ini. <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/10-film-tentang-time-traveling-ini-wajib-kamu-tonton-yang-ke-8-dari-indonesia-loh/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Petualangan Marty McFly dan Doc Brown mengarungi waktu</a> bersama mobil-rangkap-mesin-waktu DMC Delorean menjadi salah satu film yang memberikan fantasi masa depan bagi penonton di masanya. Jika Blade Runner memberikan inspirasi masa depan yang suram, gelap, dan dingin; maka Back To The Future punya gambaran masa depan yang sangat <em>funky</em>.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_41410\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41410\" data-attachment-id=\"41410\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/10-film-tentang-time-traveling-ini-wajib-kamu-tonton-yang-ke-8-dari-indonesia-loh/attachment/traveling6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Tidak ada Hoverboard di tahun 2015 kita. Sumber gambar: io9.gizmodo.com\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-41410\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41410\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Asyiknya bermain hoverboard. (Sumber: Gizmodo)</p></div></p>\n<p>Simak saja Back To The Future Part 2, dengan segala nuansa <em>retro futurism</em> mereka. Pandangan orang 80-an tentang masa depan di tahun 2015 sangatlah berwarna dan ajaib. Nggak ada <em>skateboard</em>, melainkan <em>hoverboard</em> yang sangat keren. Mobil-mobil turut melayang di udara. Sepatu Nike bisa menalikan dirinya sendiri. Benar-benar sebuah gambaran masa depan yang keren!</p>\n<p>Puluhan tahun berselang, dan kini sudah tahun 2018. Nike berhasil membuat sepatu dengan fungsi yang sama di film, dan Pepsi meramu Pepsi Perfect dalam jumlah terbatas. Namun <em>hoverboard</em> yang dijanjikan belum kunjung datang. 2015 versi Back To The Future berbeda dengan 2015 yang nyata. Meski begitu, bro sis yang suka Back To The Future bisa kembali menikmati petualangan Marty dan Doc Brown lewat komik <em>manga</em> terbaru!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42652\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42652\" data-attachment-id=\"42652\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kembali-ke-masa-depan-lewat-manga-back-to-the-future/attachment/01-manga-back-to-the-future/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/01-manga-back-to-the-future.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01 manga back to the future\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/01-manga-back-to-the-future-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/01-manga-back-to-the-future.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42652\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/01-manga-back-to-the-future.jpg\" alt=\"01 manga back to the future\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/01-manga-back-to-the-future.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/01-manga-back-to-the-future-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42652\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Back to the Future versi manga. (Sumber: Anime News Network)</p></div></p>\n<p>Dilaporkan bahwa <a href=\"https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2018-02-01/one-punch-man-artist-yuusuke-murata-to-launch-manga-based-on-back-to-the-future-film/.127228#QrOoV8yiGYQsOTr7.01\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>manga</em> Back To The Future akan dirilis</a>, yang nantinya akan menampilkan cerita-cerita baru dan berbeda dari tiga film Back To The Future yang sudah ada. Nantinya <em>manga</em> ini akan digambar oleh Yusuke Murata yang populer lewat Eyeshield 21 dan One Punch Man. Bro sis pastinya sudah kenal dengan dua judul <em>manga</em> dan <em>anime</em> tersebut, kan?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42653\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42653\" data-attachment-id=\"42653\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kembali-ke-masa-depan-lewat-manga-back-to-the-future/attachment/02-bob-gale/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/02-bob-gale.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02 bob gale\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/02-bob-gale-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/02-bob-gale.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42653\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/02-bob-gale.jpg\" alt=\"02 bob gale\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/02-bob-gale.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/02-bob-gale-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42653\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Bob Gale. (Sumber: The Hollywood Reporter)</p></div></p>\n<p>Nah, selain Yusuke Murata, ada pula sosok Bob Gale sebagai <em>supervisor</em> cerita. Gale adalah penulis naskah untuk film Back To The Future, dan keterlibatannya akan memastikan <em>manga</em> Back To The Future ini bakalan setia dan otentik dengan tiga film yang menginspirasinya.</p>\n<p>Beberapa poster telah dirilis untuk mempromosikan manga Back To The Future. Poster pertama di atas menampilkan ilustrasi karakter yang diciptakan oleh Murata. Bro sis bisa melihat karakter-karakter dari tiga film Back To The Future digabung dalam satu gambar. Sementara gambar poster kedua menampilkan mobil Delorean yang tengah memulai proses perjalanan waktunya. Poster tersebut bakal membuka <em>chapter</em> pertama dari <em>manga</em> tersebut.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42654\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42654\" data-attachment-id=\"42654\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kembali-ke-masa-depan-lewat-manga-back-to-the-future/attachment/03-delorean/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/03-delorean.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03 delorean\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/03-delorean-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/03-delorean.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42654\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/03-delorean.jpg\" alt=\"03 delorean\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/03-delorean.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/03-delorean-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42654\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Delorean milik Doc melesat mengarungi waktu. (Sumber: Anime News Network)</p></div></p>\n<p>Ditemui dalam <em>event</em> film Ready Player One di Tokyo pada hari Kamis lalu, Murata mengaku tertantang dalam mengadaptasi Back To The Future ke dalam media <em>manga</em>. Secara spesifik, ia menganggap menggambar wajah Marty yang diperankan Michael J. Fox ini sebagai tantangan yang sulit dilalui. Meski demikian, Murata tetap bakal berusaha keras dalam menggambar <em>manga</em>.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42655\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42655\" data-attachment-id=\"42655\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kembali-ke-masa-depan-lewat-manga-back-to-the-future/attachment/04-marty/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/04-marty.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04 marty\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/04-marty-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/04-marty.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42655\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/04-marty.jpg\" alt=\"04 marty\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/04-marty.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/04-marty-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42655\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Michael J. Fox, 30 tahun lalu dan masa kini. (Sumber: Digital Spy)</p></div></p>\n<p>Saat ini Yusuke Murata masih mengerjakan <em>manga</em> Back To The Future. Rencananya <em>manga</em> ini akan diterbitkan di Jepang lewat <em>website</em> Kono Manga ga Sugoi. Selain itu, Murata juga akan memproduksi versi cetaknya yang direncanakan terbit pada tanggal 20 April 2018.</p>\n<p>Mungkin masih butuh waktu lama agar kita bisa menikmati teknologi mesin waktu, mobil terbang, serta <em>hoverboard</em>. Tapi dengan <em>manga</em> Back To The Future, setidaknya menunggu datangnya masa depan akan jadi sedikit lebih asyik!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"61dc281f-76d2-5955-96d5-7377c5353253"}}}